24
00:07:01.505 --> 00:07:03.507
<i>That's when I realized
that I'd made a mistake.</i>

25
00:07:04.174 --> 00:07:06.844
You know? It was a trap.
They brought me there to kill me.

26
00:07:07.553 --> 00:07:11.366
